&lt;p microsoft=&quot;&quot; yahei=&quot;&quot; light=&quot;&quot; simsun=&quot;&quot; arial=&quot;&quot; sans-serif=&quot;&quot; justify=&quot;&quot; normal=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;为宇航员提供动能&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
